<seg rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em"><seg rend="o-midashi" rendition="h"><seg rend="midashi_anchor" rendition="a" xml:id="midashi100">田舎乙女</seg></seg></seg>
<lb />
おまへは田舎の<lb />
乙女さま<lb />
<lb />
